Mothercare Says Ben Gordon to Step Down as Chief Executive

-- B y   M a r i a   E r m a k o v a
-- 
2011-10-11T12:02:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-11/mothercare-says-ben-gordon-to-step-down-as-chief-executive.html
Mothercare Plc (MTC)  said Ben Gordon will
step down from his role as chief executive officer on Nov. 17
“by mutual consent.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
